"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The scorpion makes three attacks: two with its claws and "
"one with its sting.    \n"
"**Claw.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"6 (1d8 + 2) bludgeoning damage, and the target is grappled (escape DC "
"12). The scorpion has two claws, each of which can grapple only one target.    "
"\n"
"**Sting.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"creature. _Hit:_ 7 (1d10 + 2) piercing damage, and the target must make a DC "
"12 Constitution saving throw, taking 22 (4d10) poison damage on a failed "
"save, or half as much damage on a successful one. \n"
msgstr ""
